git-twin
========

## Just do it!

```
$ ./install.sh
```

## Clone

```
$ git clone https://github.com/kaneshin/git-twin.sh ~/.git-twin.sh
```


## Settings

```
# .shrc
if [[ -s "$HOME/.git-twin.sh/twin.sh" ]]; then
    source ~/.git-twin.sh/twin.sh
    alias git-twin='_git_twin'
fi
```

```
# .gitconfig
[alias]
	twin = !sh -c 'source ~/.git-twin.sh/twin.sh && _git_twin \"$0\" \"$1\"'
```


